title: RIP MY SHRED STICK: HUNTINGTON BEACH
description: Today was a day for the Rip My Shred Stick history books. A pumping six-to-eight foot swell kept competitors on their toes and also in tip top shape. Along with the plenty of paddling and closeout sets on the head, there were some crazy, memorable rides that went down at 9th Street in H.B. Click into the story for full highlights and photos from RMSS Huntington Beach. Photos/video: PK.

asset.author: Hurley
